# Word Deletion Test
# Tests Cmd+Backspace to delete words
Output examples/dvds/word-deletion-test.svg

Set Width 800
Set Height 400
Set FontSize 16
Set Theme monokai
Set Title "Word Deletion Test"
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[32m$\x1b[0m "

Type "hello world example text"
Sleep 500ms

# Delete "text" with Cmd+Backspace
Cmd+Backspace
Sleep 500ms

# Delete "example "
Cmd+Backspace
Sleep 500ms

# Delete "world "
Cmd+Backspace
Sleep 500ms

Enter
Sleep 1s
